":60,"height":60}}},"relatedPosts":[],"structuredBody":{"blocks":[{"__typename":"DatoCmsArticleBodyImage","id":"30114775","image":{"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[],"fallback":{"src":"https://www.datocms-assets.com/66479/1651771127-thinking-about-wlb-img1.jpg?auto=format&w=860","srcSet":"https://www.datocms-assets.com/66479/1651771127-thinking-about-wlb-img1.jpg?auto=format&dpr=0.25&w=860 215w,\nhttps://www.datocms-assets.com/66479/1651771127-thinking-about-wlb-img1.jpg?auto=format&dpr=0.5&w=860 430w,\nhttps://www.datocms-assets.com/66479/1651771127-thinking-about-wlb-img1.jpg?auto=format&w=860 860w","sizes":"(min-width: 860px) 860px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpg;base64,"},"width":860,"height":430},"alt":"thinking about wlb img1"}}],"links":[],"value":{"schema":"dast","document":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"heading","level":1,"children":[{"type":"span","value":"How much do you care about Work-Life balance?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"span","value":"The work-life balance which literally means "},{"type":"span","marks":["highlight"],"value":"the balance between work and private life"},{"type":"span","value":" is one of the \"standards\" measuring in-office culture or welfare of a company when you get a job or move to another job. Some people do really care about work-life balance for guaranteeing their own private hours or escaping out from the stresses caused by work. By the way, I noticed that there are people who don't like the term \"work-life balance\" from recent chit-chat with my colleagues. So, why do they think so?"}]},{"type":"heading","level":1,"children":[{"type":"span","value":"Why do we try to separate professional life from private life?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"span","value":"It is definitely important(I think) that maintaining a proper(yeah it's pretty ambiguous though..) balance between professional life and private life. I personally think the productivity could be going to increase when we have time to focus entirely on ourselves and the things we cherish around us, not work. I remember one day when I was in elementary school, my homeroom teacher said, \"Study hard, play hard.\" Now I come to think of it, it's kind of like a student version of work-life balance."}]},{"item":"30114775","type":"block"},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"span","value":"When we were student, we studied hard, but after we got a job, we work hard to lead our own lives. At this point, let's think about the time spending on working. It's easy to find out that we can't ignore the size of working hours, which is a big part of our lives. "},{"type":"span","marks":["highlight"],"value":"Those who are reluctant to use the word work-life balance seem to be concerned that there is room for a negative view of the big part of our lives through the word work-life balance"},{"type":"span","value":"."}]},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"type":"heading","level":1,"children":[{"type":"span","value":"What could be needed not to use the word Work-Life balance?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"span","value":"To listen"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"span","value":"(will be updated)"}]}]}}}}},"pageContext":{"id":"10992983","locale":"en"}},
